{
  "stem": "10818.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so you know, this seemed to be a nice area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we had one day to look around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, we drove to, to, to Princeton.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we couldn't find anything in Princeton that we could afford to rent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So somebody recommended something in Hopewell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we started looking around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one thing led to another.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, this is too far from the railroad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't commute from here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, it turned out that at the time, there was a-- the Reading Railroad went right through Hopewell.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it had a couple of commuter trains a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we found what was a very nice airy apartment over three garages, in a rather peculiar place in Hopewell and lived there happily for five years.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even though my mother took one look at it and said, well, maybe six weeks, until you find something else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was working at Princeton University.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a research assistant, for the same man that I had worked at Yale.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And gradually, the Yale people sort of dispersed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was the last who was still there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and I worked there until Naomi was born, our oldest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three weeks until before Naomi was born.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was born on January 24, 1953.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I quit as of December 31.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and then Eva was born there, too, in February, on February 27, 1955.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, but by that time, I really wanted to live in Princeton.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And by that time, Frank had gotten a job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we felt that we were able to swing a house, with my parents' help, I must say.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we started looking around for, for-- you know, we looked in these various developments that were even then springing up, all over Princeton.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we found this house.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
